data.meta_description: Hitler's Thirty Days to Power — Turner, Henry Ashby — A history of the fateful month that gave rise to the most destructive leader of the 20th-century. Henry Ashby Turner provides an account of the events that culminated in Adolf Hitler's taking power in January of 1933.
